# Organizr — project context

This repo builds **Organizr** (organizr.co), a multi-tenant SaaS for organizing recurring
group activities and tracking who's coming.

## Where to work (critical)

- **All product work happens in `pickup-platform/`.** This is the real Next.js 15 + Supabase app.
- The **repo root** (`src/`, `bot/`, `vite.config.ts`, etc.) is the original **"Jeff Pickup"
  proof-of-concept** (single-org, soccer-specific, Vite). It is **inspiration/reference only** —
  do NOT build product features there. It also holds deferred experiments (aura, omegaball,
  WhatsApp bot) that are out of scope.

## Restore full context

Before non-trivial work, read these (authoritative over any summary):

- `pickup-platform/docs/CONTEXT.md` — full session-restore brief (architecture, conventions, gotchas)
- `pickup-platform/docs/MVP_PLAN.md` — plan of record
- `pickup-platform/docs/TODO.md` — live task list

## Working agreements

- Verify with `npm run build` in `pickup-platform/` after substantive changes.
- Only commit/push when explicitly asked; push to `main` with concise messages.
- When using shell globs, quote paths containing `[brackets]`.
